---
title: Turkey Breast and Creamy Mustard Sauce with Arugula, Feta and Tomato Salad
description: Our velvety mustard sauce is a perfect match for turkey. It's served over a salad of peppery arugula with creamy avocados, ripe baby tomatoes and crumbly feta.
